\pard\cbpat2\nowidctlpar\li48\ri5\sb269\sl-197\slmult0\qj\cf1\lang1033\expndtw-4\fs21 In \i A Choice of Catastrophes, \i0 "Catastrophes of the First Class" \expndtw0 are those in which the whole Universe is destroyed.\cf0\lang2057\fs20\par
