\pard\cbpat2\nowidctlpar\li14\ri34\sb418\sl-202\slmult0\qj\cf1\lang1033\expndtw4 Pa had sent me out to get an extra pail of air. I'd just about \expndtw2 scooped it full and most of the warmth had leaked from my \expndtw5 fingers when I saw the thing.\cf0\lang2057\expndtw0\par
