\pard\cbpat2\nowidctlpar\fi250\li29\ri14\sb192\sl-197\slmult0\qj\cf1\lang1033\expndtw-3 In the morning Simon told me something about the Camp, \expndtw2 but not until after he had had me check the apartment for \expndtw-1 bugs. I thought at first he had been given behavior mod and gone paranoid. We never had been infested. And I'd been \expndtw0 living alone for a year and a half; surely they didn't want to \expndtw-3 hear me talking to myself? But he said, "They may have been \expndtw-2 expecting me to come here."\cf0\lang2057\expndtw0\par
